value.name: Greenacres-area man, 46, dies five days after Forest Hill Boulevard crash
value.description: GREENACRES – A Greenacres-area man died Thursday night, five days after a two-vehicle crash outside a mobile-home park on Forest Hill Boulevard, the Palm Beach County Sheriff’s Office said.
